<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Undo on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/undo/</link><description>Recent content in Undo on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/undo/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] ORA-01555: Snapshot Too Old</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/ora-01555/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/ora-01555/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ora-01555-snapshot-too-old"&gt;ORA-01555: Snapshot Too Old&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ORA-01555 occurs when a long-running query needs to read data that has been overwritten in the undo (rollback) tablespace. The undo data needed for consistent read is no longer available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The undo tablespace is too small for the workload&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A long-running query references data modified by concurrent transactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The &lt;code&gt;UNDO_RETENTION&lt;/code&gt; setting is too low&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The undo tablespace has autoextend disabled&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="increase-undo-retention"&gt;Increase Undo Retention&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SYSTEM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt; undo_retention &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3600&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- 1 hour
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="resize-the-undo-tablespace"&gt;Resize the Undo Tablespace&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/undotbs01.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; RESIZE &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- or add a new datafile
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; TABLESPACE undotbs1 &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/undotbs02.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SIZE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt; AUTOEXTEND &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="enable-guaranteed-undo-retention"&gt;Enable Guaranteed Undo Retention&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; TABLESPACE undotbs1 RETENTION GUARANTEE;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="optimize-long-running-queries"&gt;Optimize Long-Running Queries&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Break long queries into smaller batches
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Instead of:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; large_table;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Use:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; large_table &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; id &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BETWEEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AND&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100000&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; large_table &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; id &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BETWEEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100001&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AND&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;200000&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-current-undo-usage"&gt;Check Current Undo Usage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SUM&lt;/span&gt;(bytes) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; mb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dba_undo_extents
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;GROUP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Long-running report
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;/*+ PARALLEL(4) */&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; sales &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; quarter &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Q1&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- ORA-01555: snapshot too old: rollback segment number 5 with name &amp;#34;_SYSSMU5$&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Fix: increase undo_retention or optimize the query
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Concurrent DML during report
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Session 1: long query
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Session 2: DELETE FROM sales WHERE ...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Fix: use UNDO_RETENTION GUARANTEE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/ora-01652/"&gt;ORA-01652&lt;/a&gt; — temp segment extension failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/ora-08177/"&gt;ORA-08177&lt;/a&gt; — serialization access failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Oracle - ORA-01555: snapshot too old</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-flashback-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-flashback-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;ORA-01555: snapshot too old (rollback segment too small) occurs when Oracle cannot maintain a read-consistent view of data because the undo information needed by a long-running query has been overwritten by newer transactions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Long-running query spanning many DML operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UNDO tablespace too small to retain enough history&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FETCH across COMMIT in cursor operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Batch processing without periodic commits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UNDO_RETENTION too short for the workload&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check UNDO tablespace usage:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name, round(sum_bytes&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; size_gb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; (
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;sum&lt;/span&gt;(bytes) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; sum_bytes
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dba_data_files
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; v$parameter &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;undo_tablespace&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;GROUP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Increase UNDO tablespace size:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/mydb/undotbs01.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;AUTOEXTEND &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NEXT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt; MAXSIZE &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Increase UNDO retention:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SYSTEM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt; UNDO_RETENTION &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3600&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- 1 hour
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED for concurrent processing:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DECLARE&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CURSOR&lt;/span&gt; c_orders &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IS&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; order_id &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; orders &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; status &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;pending&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FOR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UPDATE&lt;/span&gt; SKIP LOCKED;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BEGIN&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FOR&lt;/span&gt; rec &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IN&lt;/span&gt; c_orders LOOP
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- process without blocking
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UPDATE&lt;/span&gt; orders &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt; status &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;processing&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; order_id &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; rec.order_id;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;COMMIT&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END&lt;/span&gt; LOOP;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="5"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize long-running queries:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Add indexes to reduce query time
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INDEX&lt;/span&gt; idx_orders_status &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; orders(status);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Use parallel query for large scans
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;/*+ PARALLEL(4) */&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; large_table;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="6"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Increase PGA for sort operations:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
